uot;:&quot;nil&quot;,&quot;469789814&quot;:&quot;nil&quot;}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span data-contrast=\"none\">Teaching, services, and research practices<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:240,&quot;335572071&quot;:0,&quot;335572072&quot;:0,&quot;335572073&quot;:4278190080,&quot;335572075&quot;:0,&quot;335572076&quot;:0,&quot;335572077&quot;:4278190080,&quot;335572079&quot;:0,&quot;335572080&quot;:0,&quot;335572081&quot;:4278190080,&quot;335572083&quot;:0,&quot;335572084&quot;:0,&quot;335572085&quot;:4278190080,&quot;335572087&quot;:0,&quot;335572088&quot;:0,&quot;335572089&quot;:4278190080,&quot;469789798&quot;:&quot;nil&quot;,&quot;469789802&quot;:&quot;nil&quot;,&quot;469789806&quot;:&quot;nil&quot;,&quot;469789810&quot;:&quot;nil&quot;,&quot;469789814&quot;:&quot;nil&quot;}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div  class=\"grid row equal   \" >\n<div  class=\"col-sm\">\n<div  class=\"card text-center inset lightgold \" style=\"width:100%\">\n<div class=\"card-body\">\n<h2 class=\"card-title\">Featured Project<\/h2>\n<div class=\"card-image-inset\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/sites.uw.edu\/neurodiversity\/files\/2026\/03\/Playbook_cover.jpg\" class=\"card-img card-img-inset\" alt=\"cupcakes\"><\/div>\n<p><strong>Autism @ Work and @Neurodiversity at Work Playbooks:<\/strong> Learn from leading employers about how to make workplaces welcoming to neurodivergent employees.<\/p>\n<p class=\"button\"><a href=\"https:\/\/sites.uw.edu\/neurodiversity\/neurodiversity-at-work-playbook\/\" class=\"btn btn-sm white \"><span>Get the Playbooks<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Our Mission The UW Institute for Neurodiversity Employment brings together leading scholars and practitioners from various disciplines to build the capacity of the UW, Washington State, and the nation to create meaningful employment